    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add your <strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>,<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>black beans</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>tomato paste</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1627388315569-x200.jpg",
