            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>drained black beans </strong>and a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 1-2 min further</p><p>Add the <strong>tomato stock</strong> to the pan and cook for 1-2 min or until the sauce has slightly reduced</p><p>Once done, mash the <strong>beans</strong> to a rough paste – this is your <strong>black bean mixture</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
