    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped coriander</strong> to a <strong>pestle & mortar </strong>with 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Grind to a paste, then add your <strong>mayo</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>coriander mayo</strong></p><p>Tip: Don't have a pestle and mortar? Just chop the coriander finely and mix it with the mayo!</p>",
